{"tid":1756779,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"方國珊套丁佔屋敗訴須賠82萬元　地主代表入稟申破產令","createTime":"2019-11-26T07:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:46:28.000Z","uid":120484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"158edf12b12297de40911dc2cfb336568b46fd30","tid":1756779,"uid":120484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:46:02.000Z","msg":"剛成功連任的西貢區議員方國珊，今年7月被高院裁定她的村屋發展計劃涉及不合法「套丁」協議，被下令要將涉案土地歸還予已故地主的遺產，及就佔用土地和建成的村屋，向地主遺產賠償82萬港元。 <br />\n<br />\n上述案件的原告、已故地主何淑明的遺產管理人關雄盛昨日(25日)入稟高院原訟庭，申請將方國珊頒令破產，司法機構已排期在明年1月15日審理此案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191126/bkn-20191126122508052-1126_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191126%2Fbkn-20191126122508052-1126_00822_001.html&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV09T2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=1d7a87f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191126/bkn-20191126122508052-1126_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"75bbd89564802a4bf19a24af2b02f40c488edc62","tid":1756779,"uid":327469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">區議會大奇跡日！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">感謝所有不分化，不割席既選民！<br />\n你地叻叻豬！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}